00:19:37,412 --> 00:19:40,415
你在嚼什麼東西？ 沒什麼
- What are you chewing? - Nothing.

169
00:19:40,667 --> 00:19:43,335
吐出來，那是什麼？
Spit that out. What is that?

170
00:19:46,004 --> 00:19:48,757
真可愛 媽？
- That's lovely. - Mom?

171
00:19:49,007 --> 00:19:51,176
我不想演只笨兔子
I don't want to be a dumb bunny.

172
00:19:51,427 --> 00:19:56,306
甜心，演戲而已 還有其它很多兔子. 會很酷的
Honey, it's a play. There's lots of other bunnies. It'll be cool.

173
00:19:56,851 --> 00:19:59,395
你瘋了，媽 那麼你告訴我
- You're bonkers, Mom. - So you tell me.

174
00:19:59,645 --> 00:20:02,731
我愛你 我也愛你. 那是什麼？
- Love you. - Love you too. What's that?

175
00:20:02,983 --> 00:20:04,983
謝謝
Thank you.

176
00:20:08,697 --> 00:20:09,697
再見
Bye.

177
00:22:15,173 --> 00:22:20,260
嗨，我是保羅·馬提爾 嗶聲後請留下你的訊息. 謝謝
Hi, this is Paul Martel. Leave a message after the beep. Thanks.

178
00:22:21,638 --> 00:22:23,264
喂？ 喂？
Hello? Hello?

179
00:22:23,848 --> 00:22:25,807
喂？ 喂？
- Hello? - Hello?

180
00:22:26,017 --> 00:22:28,478
你在哦
You're there.

181
00:22:28,686 --> 00:22:32,272
我是康妮·桑納，狂風天碰到的那個人
This is Connie Sumner, the one from the windy day.

182
00:22:32,525 --> 00:22:35,027
哦，那一個
Oh, that one.

183
00:22:36,029 --> 00:22:37,988
膝蓋如何？ 你有冰敷嗎？
How's the knee? Did you ice it?

184
00:22:38,406 --> 00:22:42,409
有的，我有冰敷且墊高腳 全照你說的去做
Yes, I iced it and I elevated it. You name it, I did it.

185
00:22:42,661 --> 00:22:47,999
好多了 我只是想打個電話跟你道謝
It's much better. I just wanted to call and thank you.

186
00:22:48,210 --> 00:22:50,921
我想問一下你的地址 因為我想要--
I wanted your address because I wanted...

187
00:22:51,171 --> 00:22:52,880
你在哪堙H 你說什麼？
- Where are you? - What?

188
00:22:53,130 --> 00:22:55,424
我說，你人在哪堙H
I said, where are you?

189
00:22:58,221 --> 00:23:01,598
我在中央車站 真的聽不太清楚你的聲音
I'm in Grand Central. It's really hard to hear you.

190
00:23:01,891 --> 00:23:04,477
過來看我 什麼？
- Come and see me. - What?

191
00:23:04,727 --> 00:23:08,106
對，過來坐一下 我煮咖啡給你喝
Yeah, take a break. I'll make you some coffee.

192
00:23:11,568 --> 00:23:13,487
咖啡？
Coffee?

193
00:23:19,744 --> 00:23:22,205
好的! 好的!
- Okay. - Okay.

194
00:23:22,622 --> 00:23:24,206
再見了
See you. Bye.

195
00:23:24,417 --> 00:23:26,042
靠!
Fuck.

196
00:23:37,639 --> 00:23:40,559
沒成了永久殘廢吧，跳給我看看
No permanent damage, I see.

197
00:23:43,479 --> 00:23:48,151
政府有醫療補助、藍十字會... 我沒投保
- We take Medicaid, Blue Cross. . . . - I'm uninsured.

198
00:23:49,069 --> 00:23:52,406
不行，恐怕我們無法接受慈善救濟
No. I'm afraid we don't take charity cases.

199
00:23:57,370 --> 00:23:59,371
開個玩笑啦!
It was a joke.

200
00:24:07,673 --> 00:24:10,926
看看這本. 傑克·倫敦著作
Look at this. Jack London.

201
00:24:11,136 --> 00:24:14,972
"白牙"的初稿，還是原始書套
First edition of White Fang, in the original dust jacket.

202
00:24:15,807 --> 00:24:18,059
我花一元五角買的
And I got it for a buck fifty.

203
00:24:18,269 --> 00:24:22,397
現在值多少呢？ 大概超過4000倍以上價錢
- What's it worth? - About 4000 times more.

204
00:24:26,152 --> 00:24:31,239
是用法文寫的 我在學校學過法文
- Those are in French. - I took it in school.

205
00:24:36,164 --> 00:24:38,499
我要脫掉嗎？
Do I want to take off something?

206
00:24:40,585 --> 00:24:44,797
你的外套. 要不要把外套脫下來？
Your coat. Would you like to take off your coat?

207
00:24:45,049 --> 00:24:47,467
好的，我的外套
Yes, my coat.

208
00:24:47,968 --> 00:24:49,887
謝謝
Thank you.

209
00:24:57,687 --> 00:25:02,150
但我不能待太久 我還有些事要辦
But I can't stay very long. I have some errands I have to run.

210
00:25:03,026 --> 00:25:06,154
我去沖咖啡 好的
- I'll get the coffee. - Okay.

211
00:25:27,429 --> 00:25:31,098
那是點字書 點字
- It's in Braille. - Braille.

212
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:34,353
不，不，布萊爾 他是法國人
No, no, Braille. He was French.

213
00:25:35,647 --> 00:25:37,440
閉上眼睛
Close your eyes.

214
00:25:37,690 --> 00:25:41,192
什麼？ 閉上眼睛
- What? - Close your eyes.

215
00:25:55,461 --> 00:25:58,714
「我母親為我燉了隻雞
My mother makes me chicken

216
00:26:01,425 --> 00:26:05,052
吃了她的雞讓我咳嗽不已
Her chicken makes me cough

217
00:26:06,431 --> 00:26:09,142
我希望她在燉的時候
I wish that when she made it

218
00:26:09,935 --> 00:26:13,021
能把雞毛拔乾淨」
She took the feathers off

219
00:26:18,152 --> 00:26:20,738
書上不是那麼寫的
It doesn't say that.

220
00:26:23,117 --> 00:26:24,700
(烹飪之樂)

221
00:26:30,041 --> 00:26:32,627
我最好走了 什麼？
- I had better go. - Yeah?

222
00:26:32,877 --> 00:26:35,088
我最好走了
I'd better go.

223
00:26:39,928 --> 00:26:42,097
小心，別跌倒了
Take care. Don't fall.

224
00:26:42,304 --> 00:26:47,476
謝謝你的咖啡 你還沒喝呢
- Thanks for the coffee. - You didn't drink it.

225
00:27:03,663 --> 00:27:06,791
林賽，嗨 康妮
- Lindsay, hi. - Connie.

226
00:27:07,041 --> 00:27:09,127
我通知他一下 謝謝
- Let me buzz him. - Thanks.

227
00:27:11,838 --> 00:27:15,799
嘿，真是意外. 看看你
Hey, what a surprise. Look at you.

228
00:27:16,009 --> 00:27:17,635
嗨，比爾 嗨，康妮
- Hi, Bill. - Hi, Connie.

229
00:27:17,845 --> 00:27:20,263
我打擾到你們嗎？ 不，我正要離開
- Am I interrupting? - No, I'm leaving.

230
00:27:20,515 --> 00:27:23,892
我晚點拿預算案給你 好的，謝謝
- I'll get you the budget later. - All right, thanks.

231
00:27:24,143 --> 00:27:27,644
要喝杯咖啡嗎？ 不用了，謝謝
- Would you like a coffee? - No, thank you.

232
00:27:33,529 --> 00:27:35,655
太好了
That's nice.

233
00:27:37,658 --> 00:27:40,745
我不知道你今天要來
I didn't know you were coming in today.

234
00:27:40,995 --> 00:27:43,413
你冷死了 那是什麼？
You're freezing. What is that?

235
00:27:43,665 --> 00:27:47,168
我在轉角附近，就幫你帶了件禮物
I was around the corner and I brought you a present.

236
00:27:47,378 --> 00:27:50,047
哇. 是什麼特別日子嗎？
Wow. What's the occasion?

237
00:27:50,214 --> 00:27:53,092
沒有. 我不知道
Nothing. I don't know.

238
00:27:53,427 --> 00:27:56,846
是中碼的，但店員說會越穿越松
It's a medium, but they said it runs large.

239
00:27:57,389 --> 00:28:00,517
看看那個 你不必現在穿上
- Look at that. - You don't have to try it on.

240
00:28:00,976 --> 00:28:04,021
我是老闆，我高興怎樣就怎樣
I'm the boss. I can do whatever I want.

241
00:28:11,738 --> 00:28:13,530
你覺得怎樣？
What do you think?

242
00:28:15,284 --> 00:28:17,620
等我一下
Hold on just a second.

243
00:28:18,746 --> 00:28:20,497
是的？
Yeah?

244
00:28:22,417 --> 00:28:24,711
好的，其它電話暫時不接了
Okay, but hold the other calls.

245
00:28:25,420 --> 00:28:27,129
你在忙，我先走了 坐一下
- You're busy. I'll go. - Sit.

246
00:28:27,340 --> 00:28:29,466
我要走了 不，坐下
- I'll go. - No, sit.

247
00:28:29,842 --> 00:28:33,887
你好，亨利？ 那到底是什麼問題停擺了？
Hello, Henry? So, what is this suspension problem?

248
00:28:34,138 --> 00:28:36,556
不，我沒收到
No, I never received it.

249
00:28:37,935 --> 00:28:40,978
好，送過來給我
Well, get it to me.

250
00:28:41,605 --> 00:28:46,150
那還不夠好 我坐在這堿\等，200台卡車動彈不得
It's not good enough. I'm sitting here with 200 trucks I can't use.

251
00:28:46,401 --> 00:28:50,322
好，安排個時間見面 我要法蘭克·博朋在場
Well, set up a meeting. And I want Frank Birnbaum there.

252
00:28:50,573 --> 00:28:55,328
因為我交待別人辦事，就得辦好才成
Because when I tell someone to do something, I want it done.

253
00:28:55,578 --> 00:28:57,412
我相信你會的
I'm sure you will.

254
00:29:02,420 --> 00:29:05,381
你還得辦什麼事嗎？
So, what else you up to?

255
00:29:06,049 --> 00:29:09,969
拍賣會 是嗎？ 你看中了誰？
- Auction. - Yeah? Who'd you hit on?

256
00:29:12,305 --> 00:29:15,266
隨便猜猜
The usual suspects.

257
00:29:16,645 --> 00:29:18,395
誰？
Who?

258
00:29:20,357 --> 00:29:23,984
鮑伯·蓋洛德 鮑伯？
- Bob Gaylord. - Bob?

259
00:29:24,820 --> 00:29:28,864
叫鮑伯做擔保 他們應該派你到中東去
Get Bob to pledge and they should send you to the Middle East.

260
00:29:34,831 --> 00:29:36,957
說吧
So tell me.

261
00:29:38,502 --> 00:29:40,378
什麼？
What?

262
00:29:41,506 --> 00:29:44,467
你覺得怎樣？ 有像老闆吧
What do you think? It's a keeper.

263
00:30:49,832 --> 00:30:52,625
哈囉 哈囉
- Hello. - Hello.

264
00:30:57,883 --> 00:31:02,262
我又來了. 我帶了些鬆餅
Here I am again. I brought muffins.

265
00:31:17,280 --> 00:31:20,408
這首是什麼音樂？ 你喜歡嗎？
- What is this music? - Do you like it?

266
00:31:20,658 --> 00:31:22,452
是的
Yes.

267
00:31:23,953 --> 00:31:26,831
想跳支舞嗎？
Do you want to dance?

268
00:31:27,082 --> 00:31:29,209
現在？ 是的
- Now? - Yeah.

269
00:31:31,086 --> 00:31:32,545
好的
Okay.

270
00:31:35,925 --> 00:31:41,263
我必須警告你，由我來帶舞 當然，你是美國人
- I have to warn you, I tend to lead. - Of course. You are American.

271
00:31:51,985 --> 00:31:56,448
你以前跳過？ 什麼？
- You've done this before. - What?

272
00:31:58,618 --> 00:32:01,369
你交過幾個女朋友？
How many girlfriends have you had?

273
00:32:05,626 --> 00:32:07,418
兩個
Two.

274
00:32:07,669 --> 00:32:12,048
真的？ 我會騙你嗎？
- Really? - Would I lie to you?

275
00:32:12,508 --> 00:32:15,093
不知道. 你會嗎？
I don't know. Would you?

276
00:32:33,198 --> 00:32:38,995
你的眼睛真漂亮，你應該連晚上都別閉上
Your eyes are amazing. You should never shut them, not even at night.

277
00:32:39,247 --> 00:32:42,666
你應學會張著眼睛睡覺
You should learn to sleep with your eyes open.

278
00:32:44,545 --> 00:32:49,048
我可以辦的到 你能嗎？ 〔歌聲〕你能能能.....
- I'll work on that. - Will you?

279
00:32:52,719 --> 00:32:54,680
等一下
Hang on.

280
00:32:58,726 --> 00:33:01,271
我想這是錯誤的
I think this is a mistake.

281
00:33:03,606 --> 00:33:08,653
根本沒有錯誤，全看你願不願意而已
There are no mistakes. There's what you do, and what you don't do.

282
00:33:09,531 --> 00:33:11,867
我不能這樣
I can't do this.

283
00:33:24,715 --> 00:33:27,216
我忘了外套
Forgot my coat.

284
00:35:43,245 --> 00:35:44,703
不行 怎麼？
- I can't. - What?

285
00:35:45,038 --> 00:35:46,079
怎麼回事？
What's wrong?

286
00:35:46,331 --> 00:35:49,042
我不知道怎麼辦 這是不對的
I don't know how to do this. It's wrong.

287
00:35:49,251 --> 00:35:51,419
打我 什麼？
- Hit me. - What?

288
00:35:51,836 --> 00:35:52,836
打我
Hit me.

289
00:35:59,471 --> 00:36:00,555
打我
Hit me.

290
00:37:35,913 --> 00:37:37,705
嗨，愛德華 嗨，鮑伯
- Hey, Ed. - Hey, Bob.

291
00:37:37,956 --> 00:37:40,000
好一陣子沒看到你了 沒錯
- Haven't seen you in a while. - No.

292
00:37:40,209 --> 00:37:44,086
這禮拜我一直工作到很晚 真的？ 孩子怎麼樣？
- I've been working late this week. - Really? How's the boy?

293
00:37:44,339 --> 00:37:46,048
他的生日到了 幾歲了？
- It's his birthday. - How old?

294
00:37:46,299 --> 00:37:47,299
9歲
Nine.

295
00:37:47,635 --> 00:37:50,303
那要不要全副武裝來個大搶劫？
So any major armed robberies?

296
00:37:50,512 --> 00:37:52,972
不. 不，這禮拜不行
No. No, not this week.

297
00:37:53,223 --> 00:37:55,892
說到這點，多注意一下康妮
Speaking of which, watch out for Connie.

298
00:37:56,143 --> 00:37:59,396
她會叫你在你的抵押單據上簽名 什麼？
- She'll have you sign over your mortgage. - What?

299
00:37:59,647 --> 00:38:03,274
她有設法說服你捐款嗎？ 沒有
- Did she try to hit on you for money? - No.

300
00:38:03,526 --> 00:38:08,280
我以為她跟你提過 關於學校拍賣會的事，或者別的
I thought she talked to you about this school auction, or whatever.

301
00:38:08,532 --> 00:38:09,740
沒跟我提過
Not me.

302
00:38:09,991 --> 00:38:13,077
我一直出差在外 也許她跟瑪吉說過
I've been out of town. Maybe she talked to Maggie.

303
00:38:14,331 --> 00:38:16,707
是的，我想是我搞錯了
Yeah, I guess I got it wrong.

304
00:38:16,958 --> 00:38:19,085
總之，我們欠你一頓飯
Anyway, we owe you a dinner.

305
00:38:20,921 --> 00:38:22,296
沒錯
Yeah.

306
00:38:31,642 --> 00:38:33,059
他不在
He's out.

307
00:38:35,979 --> 00:38:37,647
要不要帶東西給你？
Can I get you anything?

308
00:38:37,898 --> 00:38:40,859
不. 不，我很好，謝謝
No. No, I'm fine, thanks.

309
00:38:44,447 --> 00:38:47,492
今天辛苦了？ 不，不太會
- Tough day? - No, not really.

310
00:38:49,661 --> 00:38:52,580
你呢？ 你今天過的如何？
What about you? How was your day?

311
00:38:53,082 --> 00:38:54,540
很好
It was good.

312
00:38:54,793 --> 00:38:57,504
你知道，就平常那些瑣事
You know, the usual stuff.

313
00:39:04,469 --> 00:39:06,596
你確定不要點什麼嗎？
Sure you don't want anything?

314
00:39:06,973 --> 00:39:08,431
不用
No.

315
00:39:09,850 --> 00:39:12,227
康妮？ 什麼事？
- Con? - Yeah?

316
00:39:13,521 --> 00:39:14,646
你愛我嗎？
Do you love me?

317
00:39:16,191 --> 00:39:18,734
我當然愛你
Of course I love you.

318
00:39:19,778 --> 00:39:22,280
真是個傻問題
What a silly question.

319
00:39:23,365 --> 00:39:24,741
我猜...
I guess. . .

320
00:39:24,993 --> 00:39:27,661
...我是覺得我有點傻
. . .I'm just feeling silly.

321
00:39:32,667 --> 00:39:34,668
我馬上上去
I'll be up in a minute.

322
00:39:35,254 --> 00:39:36,880
好的
Okay.

323
00:39:37,507 --> 00:39:39,216
哦，抱歉
Oh, sorry.

324
00:41:43,689 --> 00:41:45,733
你來這堸竣偵礡H
What are we doing here?

325
00:41:47,234 --> 00:41:49,110
吃午餐啊!
Having lunch.

326
00:41:51,072 --> 00:41:54,743
我不應該這樣 你不應該吃午餐嗎？
- I shouldn't be doing this. - You shouldn't have lunch?

327
00:41:55,870 --> 00:41:58,079
不是跟你
Not with you.

328
00:41:58,289 --> 00:42:00,499
我想我們應該離開
I think we should leave.

329
00:42:05,964 --> 00:42:07,423
聽著
Listen.

330
00:42:07,633 --> 00:42:10,718
看到那邊正要買單的人沒？
See those guys over there paying the check?

331
00:42:13,096 --> 00:42:16,141
看到了 好的. 如果是右邊的人付錢...
- Yes. - Okay. If the guy on the right pays. . .

332
00:42:16,392 --> 00:42:20,270
...我們馬上離開 如果是左邊的人付錢的話...
. . .we leave right now. If the guy on the left pays. . .

333
00:42:20,563 --> 00:42:22,357
...我們就留下來
. . .we stay.

334
00:42:24,653 --> 00:42:26,612
而且我要吻你
And I kiss you.

335
00:42:27,321 --> 00:42:28,947
不
No.

336
00:42:36,415 --> 00:42:38,166
賬單給我
Give me that.

337
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:42,295
我贏了
I win.

338
00:42:45,968 --> 00:42:48,470
不 這就是生活
- No. - C'est la vie.

339
00:42:48,846 --> 00:42:51,890
別那樣. 不要
Don't do it. Don't.

340
00:44:06,642 --> 00:44:09,520
雙人房？ 當然
- Room for two? - Of course.

341
00:44:46,562 --> 00:44:49,273
音樂很好聽. 是什麼音樂？
Nice music. What is it?

342
