Has something happened? You think he's all right?

689
01:35:44,984 --> 01:35:47,650
一時還很難說
It's hard to say at this point.

690
01:35:47,862 --> 01:35:49,820
我們正在調查
We're working on it.

691
01:35:51,280 --> 01:35:55,155
總之，謝謝. 謝謝你抽空回答 謝謝
- Anyway, thanks. Thanks for your time. - Thank you.

692
01:35:55,408 --> 01:35:59,407
我喜歡這種玻璃雪花的玩意 我兒子就有一些
I like these snow-glass things. My boy has some of these.

693
01:35:59,620 --> 01:36:03,411
如果有他消息的話，麻煩通知我們 沒問題
- If you hear from him, let us know. - Certainly.

694
01:36:31,100 --> 01:36:33,348
爸! 警察今天來我們家
Dad! Cops came to our house today.

695
01:36:35,811 --> 01:36:37,436
警察？ 他們來做什麼？
Cops? What did they want?

696
01:36:42,232 --> 01:36:43,230
有人失蹤了
Someone's missing.

697
01:36:43,735 --> 01:36:46,609
他們必須詢問每個人，你知道的
And they have to check everyone, you know.

698
01:36:50,990 --> 01:36:52,029
誰失蹤了？
Who was it?

699
01:36:53,325 --> 01:36:55,450
甜心，坐好
Honey, sit up straight.

700
01:36:58,246 --> 01:37:01,456
誰失蹤了？ 我想你不認識他
- Who was it? - I don't think you know him.

701
01:37:01,664 --> 01:37:03,706
是個賣書的
He sells books.

702
01:37:03,915 --> 01:37:05,831
我忘了在哪見過他
I forget where I met him.

703
01:37:06,711 --> 01:37:09,168
他是個壞蛋嗎，媽？
Was it a bad guy, Mom?

704
01:37:11,631 --> 01:37:14,964
警察為什麼要給你問話？
Why did they want to talk to you?

705
01:37:15,172 --> 01:37:18,256
我猜他有我的名字和電話號碼
I guess he had my name and number.

706
01:37:19,635 --> 01:37:22,720
他為何會有你的電話號碼？
Why would he have your number?

707
01:37:23,389 --> 01:37:25,636
我想是跟他買過書的關係
I think I bought a book from him.

708
01:37:38,022 --> 01:37:41,146
小心點. 慢慢來 嘿，查理!
- Be careful. Take it easy. - Hey, Charlie!

709
01:37:41,526 --> 01:37:44,358
哦，親愛的 哦，我希望你住近一點
Oh, my darling. Oh, I wished you lived closer.

710
01:37:48,738 --> 01:37:53,154
主啊，感謝您賜給我們食物 以及您的恩寵
Lord, bless this food to our use, and us to thy service.

711
01:37:53,951 --> 01:37:58,243
提醒我們去幫助別人，阿門
And help us be ever mindful of the needs of others. Amen.

712
01:37:58,454 --> 01:38:00,536
阿門
Amen.

713
01:38:00,748 --> 01:38:02,498
很好，愛德華
Very nice, Edward.

714
01:38:12,880 --> 01:38:14,170
好了!
All right!

715
01:38:22,931 --> 01:38:26,763
我說個你們不知道的愛德華的事 靠過來一點
I have a story you don't know about Edward. Gather close.

716
01:39:14,675 --> 01:39:16,631
你好，桑納太太
Hello, Mrs. Sumner.

717
01:39:16,844 --> 01:39:20,885
很抱歉週末還來打擾你們 我是狄恩警探
Sorry to bother you on the weekend. I'm Detective Dean.

718
01:39:21,097 --> 01:39:23,554
這位是米羅尼克警探，紐約警探 好的
- This is Detective Mirojnick, N.Y.P.D. - Okay.

719
01:39:23,764 --> 01:39:27,014
我們希望能跟你談個幾分鐘
We were hoping to talk to you for a few minutes.

720
01:39:27,600 --> 01:39:28,725
沒問題
Sure.

721
01:39:28,935 --> 01:39:31,809
查理，我們上去走廊那邊一下 我可以過去嗎？
- Charlie, we're going up on the porch. - Can I come?

722
01:39:32,061 --> 01:39:36,353
不行，甜心. 待在外面 跟波比玩一下，我們馬上回來
No, sweetheart. Stay out here. Play with Poppy, we'll be right back.

723
01:39:37,149 --> 01:39:41,064
不知道您老婆有沒有提過 上星期我們有來過
I don't know if your wife mentioned, we were here a week ago.

724
01:39:41,277 --> 01:39:42,567
調查保羅·馬提爾的事
About Paul Martel.

725
01:39:42,778 --> 01:39:44,694
有的，失蹤了的人
Yeah, the man who was missing.

726
01:39:44,904 --> 01:39:50,571
嗯，他不會再失蹤了 屍體上週末被人發現了
Well, he's not missing anymore. His body was discovered last weekend.

727
01:39:51,119 --> 01:39:53,033
天啊，太可怕了
God, that's terrible.

728
01:39:55,996 --> 01:39:57,202
哦，我的天啊
Oh, my God.

729
01:39:57,415 --> 01:40:01,747
你想起來在哪見到馬提爾先生了嗎 桑納太太？
Do you recall where you met Mr. Martel, Mrs. Sumner?

730
01:40:02,418 --> 01:40:05,125
我說過了 不，夫人，你沒說過
- I told you. - No, ma'am, you didn't.

731
01:40:05,335 --> 01:40:07,377
對不起
I'm sorry.

732
01:40:07,587 --> 01:40:09,418
我想不起來
I can't remember.

733
01:40:10,048 --> 01:40:11,921
我想大概是募捐者吧
A fundraiser, I think.

734
01:40:12,133 --> 01:40:13,883
你能說的更詳細點嗎？
Can you be more specific?

735
01:40:14,092 --> 01:40:15,090
茱利亞德
Juilliard.

736
01:40:17,427 --> 01:40:18,509
茱利亞德？
Juilliard?

737
01:40:19,429 --> 01:40:20,511
音樂學校
The music school.

738
01:40:21,348 --> 01:40:25,181
是的，我知道茱利亞德是什麼 你當然知道. 抱歉
- Yes, I know what Juilliard is. - Of course you do. I'm sorry.

739
01:40:25,434 --> 01:40:27,558
你也去過嗎，先生？
Were you there too, sir?

740
01:40:29,020 --> 01:40:31,811
是的. 是的，我想我去過
Yes. Yes, I think I was.

741
01:40:32,021 --> 01:40:34,519
嗯，也許你見過馬提爾先生
Well, maybe you met Mr. Martel.

742
01:40:36,149 --> 01:40:38,065
不. 不，就我記得沒見過
No. No, not that I remember.

743
01:40:38,319 --> 01:40:40,484
也許你會認得他
Maybe you'd recognize him.

744
01:40:41,486 --> 01:40:43,610
不，我從沒見過他
No, I've never met him before.

745
01:40:43,821 --> 01:40:46,570
是他嗎？ 是的. 是的
- Is that him? - Yes. Yes.

746
01:40:47,491 --> 01:40:50,156
你曾到過他的公寓？
You ever been to his apartment?

747
01:40:50,326 --> 01:40:51,741
沒有
No.

748
01:40:51,951 --> 01:40:53,617
沒有，我幾乎不認識他
No, I hardly knew him.

749
01:40:53,829 --> 01:40:57,704
我不知道他為何會有我的電話號碼 也許他喜歡你
- I didn't know why he had my number. - Maybe he liked you.

750
01:40:57,917 --> 01:40:59,706
聽著，夠了
Look, that's enough.

751
01:41:03,044 --> 01:41:06,710
所以你從未到過他的公寓 那附近地區呢？
So you've never been to his apartment. How about the neighborhood?

752
01:41:06,921 --> 01:41:08,586
逛過那媔隉H 沒有
- Hang out down there? - No.

753
01:41:08,839 --> 01:41:10,589
不，不常...
No, not often. . .

754
01:41:10,800 --> 01:41:11,798
...還是不，從來沒有
. . .or no, never.

755
01:41:12,009 --> 01:41:15,884
從來沒有 我不記得上回到蘇活區是什麼時候了
Never. I can't remember the last time I was in SoHo.

756
01:41:16,095 --> 01:41:18,136
事實上是四個星期前
It was four weeks ago, actually.

757
01:41:20,972 --> 01:41:25,180
你有一張馬提爾公寓前的停車券 上面日期是四星期前
You got a parking ticket in front of Martel's apartment, four weeks ago.

758
01:41:25,394 --> 01:41:30,644
哦，那個. 對，我跟朋友在一間小店喝咖啡
Oh, that. Right. I had coffee with friends at a little place.

759
01:41:30,855 --> 01:41:31,978
我忘了
I forgot.

760
01:41:32,189 --> 01:41:35,273
是特蕾西和莎莉 哦，是的. 是的. 對
- It was Tracy and Sally. - Oh, yeah. Yes. Yep.

761
01:41:47,326 --> 01:41:49,325
聽好...
Look. . .

762
01:41:50,493 --> 01:41:53,951
我老婆知道的全告訴你了，我也是
. . .my wife has told you everything she knows, so have I.

763
01:41:54,870 --> 01:41:57,537
不介意的話，我去找我兒子
If you don't mind, we'd like to get back to our son.

764
01:41:57,709 --> 01:41:59,665
好啦
All right.

765
01:41:59,874 --> 01:42:04,166
我怎麼忘了給你我的名片呢？ 我有你的名片
- Why don't I give you my card? - I have your card.

766
01:42:05,255 --> 01:42:06,961
對啊
Right.

767
01:42:08,131 --> 01:42:10,504
祝你們週末愉快 你們也是
- Enjoy your weekend. - You too.

768
01:43:05,963 --> 01:43:08,210
桑納，拜託
Sumner, please.

769
01:43:47,077 --> 01:43:48,492
哦，天啊
Oh, my God.

770
01:43:50,078 --> 01:43:51,535
康妮？
Connie?

771
01:43:52,955 --> 01:43:54,580
嗨，特蕾西
Hi, Tracy.

772
01:43:54,791 --> 01:43:57,956
我只是來拿我今晚要穿的絲質套裝
I'm just picking up my silk suit for tonight.

773
01:43:59,959 --> 01:44:02,041
我想穿這件黑色的
I was thinking of wearing the black.

774
01:44:14,846 --> 01:44:19,345
我捐給了古德威 換別人好好亮相一番
I'm giving it to Goodwill. Let someone else be gorgeous for a change.

775
01:44:23,601 --> 01:44:27,433
估且不談我們明亮的個性 我們該帶什麼過去？
What should we bring, aside from our sparkling personalities?

776
01:44:31,316 --> 01:44:34,023
我們準備得如何了？ 很好
- How we doing? - Fine.

777
01:44:34,234 --> 01:44:37,442
要幫手嗎？ 不用
- Need help? - No.

778
01:44:38,904 --> 01:44:43,779
白酒不冰了 所以我把它放到進冰箱
Well, the white is not cold, so I'm gonna put it in the freezer.

779
01:44:44,909 --> 01:44:47,616
記得提醒我放在堶情A好嗎？
Just remind me it's in there, all right?

780
01:44:49,746 --> 01:44:52,328
大部份的人喜歡喝紅酒
Most people drink red anyway.

781
01:44:56,583 --> 01:45:00,250
我喜歡這些小玩意 還有什麼地方你們沒去過？
I love these things. Is there any place you guys haven't been?

782
01:45:00,463 --> 01:45:02,920
羅森索家有795個呢
The Rosenthals got 795 for their place.

783
01:45:03,131 --> 01:45:06,963
短短兩天就接獲六張訂單 他們正在從事招標
- In two days they had six offers. - Sealed bids is how they do it now.

784
01:45:07,175 --> 01:45:09,841
你覺得這間房子值多少，愛德華？
What do you think this place is worth, Ed?

785
01:45:10,011 --> 01:45:13,551
不清楚. 如果賣了房子，要搬去哪？
I don't know. If you sell your house, where do you go?

786
01:45:13,763 --> 01:45:17,054
以那些價錢，大溪地 曼谷
- At those prices, Tahiti. - Bangkok.

787
01:45:17,266 --> 01:45:19,763
康妮，這個是哪來的？
Connie, where is this one from?

788
01:45:30,025 --> 01:45:31,856
斐濟
Fiji.

789
01:45:32,525 --> 01:45:35,566
記住，傑夫 我要你帶我去斐濟
Remember, Jeff, I asked you to take me to Fiji.

790
01:45:35,778 --> 01:45:40,486
然後再帶我去夏威夷 每天悠閒地釣釣魚....
And then you took me to Hawaii. We went fishing every single. . . .

791
01:46:03,549 --> 01:46:05,839
怎麼了，愛德華？
What happened, Edward?

792
01:46:08,011 --> 01:46:10,009
你幹了什麼事？
What did you do?

793
01:46:11,387 --> 01:46:12,927
是你傷害他的嗎？
Did you hurt him?

794
01:46:17,515 --> 01:46:18,931
愛德華？
Edward?

795
01:46:20,352 --> 01:46:22,267
是你傷害他的嗎？
Did you hurt him?

796
01:46:24,396 --> 01:46:26,102
你做的，是不是？
You did, didn't you?

797
01:46:28,733 --> 01:46:31,231
天啊，愛德華
Jesus, Edward.

798
01:46:32,193 --> 01:46:34,440
說話呀
Talk to me.

799
01:46:34,654 --> 01:46:36,818
告訴我你做了什麼!
Tell me what you did!

800
01:46:37,030 --> 01:46:40,780
不，你告訴我你做了什麼
No, you tell me what you did.

801
01:46:41,200 --> 01:46:46,075
你是如何一而再三地和他上床 還敢騙我!
How you fucked him, over and over and over. You lied to me!

802
01:46:46,287 --> 01:46:49,745
三番兩次地 愛德華，拜託--
- Over and over and over. - Edward, please...

803
01:46:49,957 --> 01:46:51,871
不，你不用馬上回答
No, you don't talk to me now.

804
01:46:52,415 --> 01:46:54,789
我盡心盡力地付出...
I gave everything. . .

805
01:46:55,585 --> 01:46:57,750
...為了這個家
. . .for this family.

806
01:46:58,212 --> 01:46:59,377
費盡心血
Everything.

807
01:47:01,089 --> 01:47:03,336
你又做了什麼？
And what did you do?

808
01:47:04,424 --> 01:47:07,799
你像是毫無要緊地將它丟棄一旁
You threw it all away, like it was nothing.

809
01:47:08,637 --> 01:47:10,219
為什麼？
For what?

810
01:47:10,970 --> 01:47:13,176
為了那個該死的小孩
To the fucking kid.

811
01:47:21,479 --> 01:47:23,560
你以為我不知道？
You didn't think I'd know?

812
01:47:23,773 --> 01:47:27,146
我沒感覺到嗎？ 從第一天起我就曉得了
I wouldn't feel it? I knew it from the very first day.

813
01:47:29,693 --> 01:47:34,109
因為我太瞭解你了，康妮 我瞭解你卻也該死的恨你
Because I know you, Connie. I know you and I fucking hate you.

814
01:47:34,321 --> 01:47:37,903
我並不想殺他，我想殺的是你!
I didn't want to kill him, I wanted to kill you!

815
01:47:40,409 --> 01:47:42,574
哦，天啊
Oh, my God.

816
01:47:52,792 --> 01:47:56,083
愛德華. 哦，天啊
Edward. Oh, my God.

817
01:48:06,886 --> 01:48:08,885
天啊
Oh, my God.

818
01:48:50,332 --> 01:48:53,414
媽，看我做的
Mom, look what I did.

819
01:48:56,128 --> 01:49:00,544
甜心，不要緊. 不要緊的
Honey, it's okay. That's okay.

820
01:49:00,758 --> 01:49:02,131
對不起，媽
I'm sorry, Mom.

821
01:49:02,342 --> 01:49:06,300
只是意外，誰都難免有意外
It's an accident. Everybody has accidents.

822
01:49:06,510 --> 01:49:08,635
你怎不回房睡，媽？
Why aren't you in bed, Mom?

823
01:49:11,847 --> 01:49:13,180
我不知道
I don't know.

824
01:49:17,478 --> 01:49:19,018
查理，看著我
Charlie, look at me.

825
01:49:19,604 --> 01:49:21,728
我要你明白...
I want you to know. . .

826
01:49:21,940 --> 01:49:25,980
...我愛你遠勝於世上任何一切
. . .that I love you, more than anything in the world.

827
01:49:28,319 --> 01:49:31,651
我要你知道你爸和我兩個...
And I want you to know that your daddy and me both. . .

828
01:49:31,861 --> 01:49:34,318
...會永遠永遠愛你
. . .will always, always love you.

829
01:49:34,530 --> 01:49:36,778
無論如何
No matter what.

830
01:49:40,035 --> 01:49:42,825
好嗎？ 好的
- Okay? - Okay.

831
01:49:43,079 --> 01:49:44,077
好了，甜心
Come on, sweetie.

832
01:49:44,956 --> 01:49:49,664
我們把你的床整理的乾乾淨淨，好嗎？
Let's go fix up your bed all nice and fresh, okay?

833
01:49:50,042 --> 01:49:51,707
好的
All right.

834
01:53:03,429 --> 01:53:05,803
你可以上來清洗一下傷口
You can come on up and clean it off, no?

835
01:53:06,014 --> 01:53:10,472
來吧! 我不是什麼連環殺手，我發誓
Come on. I'm not an ax murderer. I promise.

836
01:53:19,689 --> 01:53:21,271
出租車!
Taxi.

837
01:53:44,207 --> 01:53:46,789
謝謝
Thank you.

838
01:54:12,896 --> 01:54:14,977
我們要怎麼辦？
What are we going to do?

839
01:54:18,149 --> 01:54:20,689
我好害怕
I'm so scared.

840
01:54:22,734 --> 01:54:23,983
我去自首
I'll turn myself in.

841
01:54:24,735 --> 01:54:26,193
不
No.

842
01:54:29,073 --> 01:54:30,573
不
No.

843
01:54:39,956 --> 01:54:42,497
不，我們會大步攬過的
No, we can get through this.

844
01:54:43,917 --> 01:54:46,582
我們一天一次，每次搬一點點
We'll take it one day at a time.

845
01:54:48,336 --> 01:54:50,417
神不知鬼不覺的
No one will know.

846
01:54:52,173 --> 01:54:54,215
而我們知道啊
We'll know.

847
01:55:02,515 --> 01:55:05,971
3200，3500，3800，4000...
3200, 3500, 3800, 4000. . .

848
01:55:06,182 --> 01:55:08,347
...42，45，4800!
. . .42, 45, 4800!

849
01:56:35,038 --> 01:56:37,287
我們可以逃的無影無蹤
We can disappear.

850
01:56:39,331 --> 01:56:41,205
可以籌一點錢
We can raise some money.

851
01:56:41,417 --> 01:56:44,541
全都賣掉，然後離開這個國家
Sell everything and just leave the country.

852
01:56:46,044 --> 01:56:47,585
小姐？
Senorita?

853
01:56:48,547 --> 01:56:50,671
墨西哥
Mexico.

854
01:56:52,133 --> 01:56:53,965
有何不可？
Why not?

855
01:56:55,717 --> 01:56:57,842
我們可以買間靠海邊的小房子
We can get a little house on the beach.

856
01:56:58,512 --> 01:57:00,553
用別的化名
Take a different name.

857
01:57:01,973 --> 01:57:03,637
大家都是這樣子做
People do it all the time.

858
01:57:04,807 --> 01:57:07,013
我們要怎麼告訴查理？
What will we tell Charlie?

859
01:57:08,896 --> 01:57:11,644
告訴他這是一次冒險
Tell him it's an adventure.

860
01:57:14,355 --> 01:57:16,728
我們可以整天釣魚
We could fish all day.

861
01:57:20,238 --> 01:57:23,322
學學如何彈吉它
We could learn to play the guitar.

862
01:57:24,655 --> 01:57:29,072
每晚對你唱小夜曲好讓你入睡
I would serenade you to sleep every night.

863
01:57:30,326 --> 01:57:33,657
就在海邊度過餘生
We'll just live the rest of our lives on that beach.

864
01:57:34,205 --> 01:57:37,496
等我們死了，就葬在海
And then when we die, we can just push out to sea.

865
01:57:38,040 --> 01:57:39,246
你認為怎樣？
What do you think?

866
01:57:42,171 --> 01:57:44,087
聽起來蠻不錯的
Sounds perfect.

